Beyond proud of my husband for winning his first boxing match last night!❤️🥊

I have never seen this level of discipline, dedication, and love towards a sport in my life. He trained 4 times a day, lost 50lbs, never cut a corner in his diet, and still would take me out on our weekly dinner dates as he would only order water. Congrats baby, it was very well deserved, and I cannot wait to see you continue this journey as this is just the beginning! God I love you so damn much🥹❤️
